quran[16]{c,v,t,f}:
  38,1,"Saad <sup>1</sup>, Waxaan (waa Alle'e) ku dhaartay Qur’aanka sharafta leh ee waanada badan <sup>2</sup>.","[1]. Eeg sharaxa hoose ee Suuradda 2 Al-Baqarah: Aayadda 1.\n[2]. Inta hadalka ka go’an waa inaysan jirin ilaahyo badan balse uu Ilaaha Xaqa yahay Mid Keliya - Allaah iyo in soo bixinta Qiyaame Xaq tahay."
  38,2,"Kuwase gaalada ahi waxay ku sugan yihiin qabwayni iyo collaytan (xaq diiddo).",""
  38,3,"Badanaa intaan halaagnay hortood facyo (Xaqa beeniyey), markaasay calaacaleen (oo tawbad keeneen) goor calaalal (tawbad keen la aqbalayn), lagana baxsan karin (Cadaabka Alle).",""
  38,4,"Waxay la yaabeen inuu u yimid dige ka mid ah (Nabi Muxammad). Waxay gaaladu yidhaahdeen: Kanu waa saaxir, beenaale.",""
  38,5,"Ma wuxuu ka dhigay ilaahyadii Ilaah Keliya? Waxakani waa wax la yaab leh.",""
  38,6,"Odayaashii ka mid ahaana way soo baxeen (iyagoo ku leh dadkoodii): Socda, oo ku samra oo sugnaada ilaahyadiinna. (arrin)kani waa wax laynala dooni <sup>3</sup>.","[3]. Uu isku soo dubbariday Muxammad si uu idiin qabsado oo magac iyo sharaf ugu qaato."
  38,7,"Weligayo kuma aanu maqal (arrin)kan oo kale diintii kale <sup>4</sup>. (Arrin)kani ma aha waxaan aheyn been abuur.","[4]. Waxay ugala jeedaan diintii kale diinta Nasaarada ama diintii shirkiga oo ay Quraysh heysatay."
  38,8,"Ma waxaa lagu soo dejiyey Qur’aanka isagoo (Muxammad) na dhex jooga? 
Mayee waxay ka shakisan yihiin Waanadeyda. Mayee, wali ma aysan dhadhamin Cadaabkayga.",""
  38,9,"Mise ma waxay hayaan khasnadaha Naxariista Rabbigaa, Adkaadaha Sare, Deeqsiga ah aad wax u bixiya?",""
  38,10,"Mise ma waxay leeyihiin Mulkiga (iyo maamulka) cirarka iyo dhulka iyo waxa u dhexeeya? Ee ha u koreen salaanno xagga 'samada hadday karaan' <sup>5</sup>.","[5]. Si ay ugu soo dejiyaan waxyiga kay doonaan. Waa dhaleeceyn iyo caajiz gelin."
  38,11,"Ciidanka halkaas jooga (gaalada) waa xisbiyo <sup>6</sup> la jabin (lagana adkaan).","[6]. Aayaddanina waxay tilmaameysaa dagaalkii Godka (Al-Axzaab) labadaba waa loo yaqaan. Mufasiriinta qaarna waxay yidhaahdeen waxay tilmaameysaa dagaalkii Badar."
  38,12,"Waxaa beeniyey (Rususha) iyaga hortood qoladii Nuux, Caad iyo Fircoon ee lahaa boqortooyo xoog leh <sup>7</sup>.","[7]. Dhismooyin dhaadheer iyo ciidammo tiro badan iyo tiirar uu dadka geeyo ciqaab ahaan."
  38,13,"Iyo Thamuud iyo qoladii Luud, iyo reer howdkii (loo diray Nabi Shucayb), kuwaa bay ahaayeen xisbiyada.",""
  38,14,"Ma jiro mid iyaga ka mid ah oo aan beenin Rususha, Markaasay xaq noqotay cadaabi inay ku dhacdo.",""
  38,15,"Kuwaana (gaaladani) ma sugayaan waxaan aheyn hal Qeylo aanan daah lahayn iyo dib u dhac midna <sup>8</sup>.","[8]. Ama fursad. Erey ahaan macnaha xiskin waa waqti u dhexeeya labada lisitaan ee caanaha hasha. Dhawaaqaas waa calaamo Qiyaamaha."
  38,16,"Waxayna yidhaahdeen: Rabbigayow! Noo soo dedeji saamigayaga (ciqaabka ) ka hor Maalinta Xisaabta (Qiyaamada).",""
